        <message_html><![CDATA[<p><img src="itsmtransform.png" alt="" width="700" height="170" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Dear ${signoff_module.key_process_owners},</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: start;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><span style="color: #666666;">You have been listed as a </span><strong><span style="color: #666666;">key</span></strong><span style="color: #666666;"> process sign-off owner for:&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="color: #666666;">${signoff_module}</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #666666; font-size: 11pt;">Please follow the steps below to ensure your part of the testing process is registered, updated and signed off correctly.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: navy;">1. Open this&nbsp;<a title="LINK" href="https://dbunity.service-now.com/x_dptmgr_deployment_signoff_list.do?sysparm_query=associated_deployment.current_release%3Dtrue%5Esignoff_module.key_process_ownersDYNAMIC90d1921e5f510100a9ad2572f2b477fe%5EORsignoff_module.engineering_contactsDYNAMIC90d1921e5f510100a9ad2572f2b477fe">LINK</a>&nbsp;to access&nbsp;your list of sign-offs specific to you to action.</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: start;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: start;">Or Copy/Paste the below URL in your browser.</p>
<p style="text-align: start;"><a href="https://dbunity.service-now.com/x_dptmgr_deployment_signoff_list.do?sysparm_query=associated_deployment.current_release%3Dtrue%5Esignoff_module.key_process_ownersDYNAMIC90d1921e5f510100a9ad2572f2b477fe%5EORsignoff_module.engineering_contactsDYNAMIC90d1921e5f510100a9ad2572f2b477fe">https://dbunity.service-now.com/x_dptmgr_deployment_signoff_list.do?sysparm_query=associated_deployment.current_release%3Dtrue%5Esignoff_module.key_process_ownersDYNAMIC90d1921e5f510100a9ad2572f2b477fe%5EORsignoff_module.engineering_contactsDYNAMIC90d1921e5f510100a9ad2572f2b477fe</a>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: start;">&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong><span style="color: navy;">2.</span> <u><span style="color: navy;">REGISTER</span></u></strong><strong><span style="color: navy;"> Your Attendance</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; color: #666666;">In your sign-off record, simply click the </span><strong><span style="color: #666666;">Register Attendance</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; color: #666666;">&nbsp;button so&nbsp;we are aware you have begun testing.</span></p>
<p><img src="registerattendance.png" alt="" width="498" height="49" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong><span style="color: navy;">3.</span> <u><span style="color: navy;">UPDATE</span></u></strong><strong><span style="color: navy;">&nbsp;Your Testing Progress</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; color: #666666;">Every hour, or sooner if possible, please provide a percentage update for the progress of your testing. This can be done by inputting a number between 0-100 in the&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="color: #666666;">Completion Progress</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; color: #666666;"> field in your sign-off record.</span></p>
<p><img src="progress.png" alt="" width="650" height="121" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><strong><span style="color: navy;">4.</span> <u><span style="color: navy;">SIGN-OFF</span></u></strong><strong><span style="color: navy;"> your Process Stream</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; color: #666666;">When you are happy to sign-off, simply click </span><strong><span style="color: #666666;">Sign Off Module</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; color: #666666;"> and it will auto-populate the required fields to indicate to us you have given sign-off.</span></p>
<p><img src="signoff.png" alt="" width="521" height="52" />&lt;/<]]></message_html>
